Instances are thread safe.

      public Config.Builder filter(Predicate<? super Class<? extends Annotation>> filter)
      Specify a filter that determines which @TypeTag meta-annotated type annotations are included.

      The default is to include all type annotations with a @TypeTag meta-annotation.

      Parameters:
